GUI Functionality Tests
Test 1
User can see a window with MTG Duel Decks at the top.

Test 2
Window is the size of the screen.

Test 3
Window is split into two sides.

Test 4
Window is split into appropriate sections for hand/library.

Test 5
Sections scale with window size.

Test 6.
Display the number of cards in library and graveyard.

Test 7.
Display cards in hand that scale with screen size.

Test 8.
Display cards on battlefield off the the side of the player that controls them.

Test 9.
Click a card in a hand to move it to the battlefield.